Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,# Come Undone 終將打開
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,## 獨白
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.83,0:00:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我這一生從未錯得如此過。\NI had never been so wrong before in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.80,0:00:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,僅僅因為我不能分享我呼吸的空氣\NFor the fact alone that\NI couldn't share the air I breathed
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.14,0:01:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我那張逐漸下垂的笑臉就多了條煩惱的皺紋\Nbrought an agonizing twitch\Nin my slowly sinking smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.28,0:01:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,儘管這聽起來很荒唐，我哭了。\NI would go as far as to say, I started to cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.11,0:01:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我也只剩下哭了。\NAnd that's just what I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.82,0:01:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,轉瞬間，我明白了，把自己關在這裡\NRight then I had realized that trapping myself here
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.02,0:01:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,是個粗魯的決定，\Nwas a rather rash decision,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.56,0:01:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,而命運不會容忍我。\Nand would not be tolerated by fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.09,0:01:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我的朋友沒了，如此，我的笑容也是。\NMy friends were gone,\Nand therefore, so is my smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.53,0:01:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我向身旁的星星訴苦，但它們不回應。\NI expressed my sorrow to the stars\Naround me, but they wouldn't respond.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.44,0:01:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,它們甚至不知道我的存在。\NThey didn't even acknowledge my presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.04,0:01:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,朋友會，但我已經沒有了。\NFriends would, but I didn't have those anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.45,0:01:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我又哭了。\NI cried again.
Comment: 0,0:01:50.42,0:01:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,## 副歌
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.46,0:01:58.13,Chorus,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}風暴席捲，在這牆內。\NThe storm is raging inside these walls.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.93,0:02:06.20,Chorus,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}心上打的詰，終將打開。\NThe knots of emotion will come undone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.94,0:02:09.77,Chorus,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}終將打開。\NCome undone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.88,0:02:14.45,Chorus,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}終將打開。\NCome undone.
